dataIdInfo.idPurp: Tools for StreamStats data pre-processing. These tools organize and modify digital elevation models and hydrography to produce a domain organized by local hydrologic units (Local Folders) and a global geodatabase. Hydro-enforced flow direction and flow accumulation grids are produced for each local hydrologic unit.
